                            Industry <br>
                            Experts
                        </h6>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="box-image rounded-12 position-relative overflow-hidden">
                    <img class="rounded-12" src="assetsClient/imgs/section/img-2.png" alt="Carento">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-12">
                <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-4 align-self-stretch h-100">
                    <div class="box-tag background-brand-2 p-5 d-flex rounded-12">
                        <span class="text-dark fs-96 me-3">25</span>
                        <h4>
                            Years in <br>
                            Business
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <img class="rounded-12" src="assetsClient/imgs/section/img-3.png" alt="Carento">
                </div>
